eLife

The eLife home automation product.

This software encompasses a Java home automation server able to talk to numerous systems including CBUS, Jandy, X10, Comfort, NESS ELK M1 and many more.

There are also some clients available, the most mature current client is the SWF flash based client, there are also clients in various stages of development for iPhone and Java.

There are several server configuration examples available in the config directory.

